VS bodies being unloaded from truck; 
MS bodies being loaded to van;
WS press conference; 
CA press;
SOT,investigator, (english): "The video tape is discovered
and observed, the informations obtained from sources, all
indicate that this was a voluntary situation...they ingested the
drugs on their own, they may or may not have been influenced, we
may never know that....in this point this is considered as mass
suicide ivestigation..";
CU journalist;
SOT,investigator, (english):" We are not going to charge
anyone with anything, and who would we charge, the drugs could
be obtained legally, so there are no charges going to be pursued
by us";
